{"sn12.45:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 12.45 ","sn12.45:0.2":"5. Gahapativagga ","sn12.45:0.3":"Natikasutta ","sn12.45:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn12.45:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava natike viharati ginjakavasathe. ","sn12.45:1.3":"Atha kho bhagava rahogato patisallano imam dhammapariyayam abhasi: ","sn12.45:2.1":"“Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.45:2.2":"Phassapaccaya vedana, ","sn12.45:2.3":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn12.45:2.4":"tanhapaccaya upadanam …pe… ","sn12.45:2.5":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.45:3.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca …pe… ","sn12.45:3.2":"ghananca paticca gandhe ca … ","sn12.45:3.3":"jivhanca paticca rase ca … ","sn12.45:3.4":"kayanca paticca photthabbe ca … ","sn12.45:3.5":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.45:3.6":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.45:3.7":"vedanapaccaya tanha; ","sn12.45:3.8":"tanhapaccaya upadanam …pe… ","sn12.45:3.9":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. ","sn12.45:4.1":"Cakkhunca paticca rupe ca uppajjati cakkhuvinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.45:4.2":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.45:4.3":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.45:4.4":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.45:4.5":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho …pe… ","sn12.45:4.6":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti. ","sn12.45:5.1":"Sotanca paticca sadde ca …pe… ","sn12.45:5.2":"mananca paticca dhamme ca uppajjati manovinnanam. Tinnam sangati phasso. ","sn12.45:5.3":"Phassapaccaya vedana; ","sn12.45:5.4":"vedanapaccaya tanha. ","sn12.45:5.5":"Tassayeva tanhaya asesaviraganirodha upadananirodho; ","sn12.45:5.6":"upadananirodha bhavanirodho …pe… ","sn12.45:5.7":"evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hoti”ti. ","sn12.45:6.1":"Tena kho pana samayena annataro bhikkhu bhagavato upassuti thito hoti. ","sn12.45:6.2":"Addasa kho bhagava tam bhikkhum upassuti thitam. ","sn12.45:6.3":"Disvana tam bhikkhum etadavoca: ","sn12.45:6.4":"“assosi no tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayan”ti? ","sn12.45:6.5":"“Evam, bhante”ti. ","sn12.45:6.6":"“Ugganhahi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam; ","sn12.45:6.7":"pariyapunahi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam; ","sn12.45:6.8":"dharehi tvam, bhikkhu, imam dhammapariyayam. ","sn12.45:6.9":"Atthasamhito ayam, bhikkhu, dhammapariyayo adibrahmacariyako”ti. ","sn12.45:6.10":"Pancamam. "}